 <span data-ttu-id="61771-237">Weitere Informationen finden Sie unter den <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> Operatoren und <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="61771-237">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
